Java-Javap
==========

Java::Javap is meant to be a Perl 6 equivalent to javah that ships with
the Java development kit.  It will translates compiled Java APIs to
corresponding Perl 6 APIs.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

USAGE

See the POD in java2perl6 (in the bin directory of the distribution) for
information on how to use this module.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    a Java development kit with javap in your path
    Parse::RecDescent

REPOSITORY

The source repository is http://github.com/timbunce/java2perl6

